<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 09 Feb 2022 12:48:40 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>最貴 NFT Bored Ape 創辦人真身曝光　被起底寫過《Warcraft》書藉</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/09/the-real-names-of-bored-ape-yacht-clubs-pseudonymous-founders/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=the-real-names-of-bored-ape-yacht-clubs-pseudonymous-founders</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 09 Feb 2022 12:48:40 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[BAYC]]></category><category><![CDATA[NFT]]></category><category><![CDATA[無聊猿]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1085359</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>NFT 數碼藝術近來可說是大行其道，當中最貴的系列無聊猿（Bored Ape Yacht Club）大家也一定 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">NFT 數碼藝術近來可說是大行其道，當中最貴的系列無聊猿（Bored Ape Yacht Club）大家也一定看到過！日前就有美國媒體透過公共商業紀錄找到該系列的創辦人 Wylie Aronow 及 Greg Solano，雖然兩人並未有正面回應，但身份已經得到 BAYC 的母公司 Yuga Labs 確認。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1085361" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3CED2B10-C069-4A60-9A5A-00C002A22084-694x468.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3CED2B10-C069-4A60-9A5A-00C002A22084-694x468.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3CED2B10-C069-4A60-9A5A-00C002A22084-768x518.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/3CED2B10-C069-4A60-9A5A-00C002A22084.jpeg 881w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1085362" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/87C4B4B5-1CF8-4C5A-864A-94FCB393A43A-694x386.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/87C4B4B5-1CF8-4C5A-864A-94FCB393A43A-694x386.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/87C4B4B5-1CF8-4C5A-864A-94FCB393A43A-1280x712.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/87C4B4B5-1CF8-4C5A-864A-94FCB393A43A-768x427.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/87C4B4B5-1CF8-4C5A-864A-94FCB393A43A-1536x854.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/87C4B4B5-1CF8-4C5A-864A-94FCB393A43A.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">美國媒體 BuzzFeed 透過發行 BAYC 母公司 Yuga Labs 的商業登記資料，發現兩位無聊猿共同創辦人。35 歲的 Aronow 來自邁阿密，專用化名為 Gordon Goner；而另一位則是現年 32 歲的 Solano，化名 Gargamel，是一位編輯及書評人，更曾與《Warcraft》設計者合著了遊戲相關書籍。在身份曝光後，Solano 和 Aronow 均沒有正面回應，但二人同時在 Twitter 貼出「 Web2 me vs Web3 me 」，二人的真實身份最終獲 Yuga Labs 行政總裁 Nicole Muniz 確認。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Got doxxed against my will. Oh well.</p><p>Web2 me vs. Web3 me <a href="https://t.co/uLkpsJ5LvN">pic.twitter.com/uLkpsJ5LvN</a></p><p>&mdash; GordonGoner.eth (@GordonGoner) <a href="https://twitter.com/GordonGoner/status/1489764541084930048?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 5, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Got doxed so why not. Web2 me vs Web3 me. <a href="https://t.co/jfmzo5NtrH">pic.twitter.com/jfmzo5NtrH</a></p><p>&mdash; Garga.eth (@CryptoGarga) <a href="https://twitter.com/CryptoGarga/status/1489768443771596800?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 5, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1085363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/63A412FC-81A2-4D0D-9F7E-4DD788A7E30C-694x460.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/63A412FC-81A2-4D0D-9F7E-4DD788A7E30C-694x460.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/63A412FC-81A2-4D0D-9F7E-4DD788A7E30C-768x510.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/63A412FC-81A2-4D0D-9F7E-4DD788A7E30C.jpeg 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">除了 Solano 和 Aronow 外，無聊猿還有兩位聯合創辦人，分別是化名為 No Sass 及 Emperor Tomato Ketchup 的兩位工程師；而設計猿人造型的藝術家，就被指是受僱於 Yuga Labs 的美藉亞裔藝術家 Seneca。無聊猿收藏品目前市值已高達 28 億美元（約港幣 218.4 億元）；即使是最便宜的收藏品，底價亦已超過 28 萬美元。製作無聊猿的公司 Yuga Labs，未來更可從交易中收取的 2.5% 的版稅。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.buzzfeednews.com/article/katienotopoulos/bored-ape-nft-founder-identity">BuzzFeed</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
