</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Lenovo 電腦情人節優惠 2022   WFH 居家抗疫合適手提電腦推介</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/09/lenovo-wfh-2022/notebook/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=lenovo-wfh-2022</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[AIpower]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 09 Feb 2022 09:30:20 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[流動電腦]]></category><category><![CDATA[買物情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[lenovo]]></category><category><![CDATA[WFH]]></category><category><![CDATA[居家抗疫]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1085044</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>情人節就快到，於 Work from Home 在家工作抗疫大趨勢之下，送一部運作流暢、方便完成工作的 WFH [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="p2">情人節就快到，於 Work from Home 在家工作抗疫大趨勢之下，送一部運作流暢、方便完成工作的 WFH 電腦，讓另一半在抗疫期間工作順利，得閒又可以一齊玩視像會議，維持緊密聯繫，可說是一舉兩得！以下會介紹一些符合不同價格預算的精選 WFH 電腦，讓你還有身邊的人好好居家抗疫。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/dlp-banner-valentines-day-1920x400-0125-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/dlp-banner-valentines-day-1920x400-0125-1-694x346.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="346" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/dlp-banner-valentines-day-1920x400-0125-1-694x346.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/dlp-banner-valentines-day-1920x400-0125-1-768x383.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/dlp-banner-valentines-day-1920x400-0125-1.jpg 802w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>Offer 1：多款精選電腦優惠</h2><h2 class="p2">入門推介：IdeaPad Slim 1</h2><p class="p2">這款 IdeaPad Slim 1 (14) 可說是較受歡迎、CP 值不錯的入門款式，入門價只需要 HK$2,768 起。此電腦內置有 AMD 處理系統，14 吋超窄邊熒幕，機身輕巧之餘續航力可達 8 小時，適合你一天工作使用。電腦更內置有 2 個支援 Dolby Audio 的揚聲器，工作完成後睇片一樣得，同時滿足工作與娛樂需要。現在購買更附送 1 年 Microsoft 365 個人版。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085046" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-1.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-s150-14-gallery-2.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2">原價：HK$3,923</p><p class="p2">售價：HK$2,768（7 折）</p><p class="p2">購買連結：<a href="https://lenovo.dgi7au.net/KanOn" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1085045 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/126046736_309199960140873_5010468024046516166_n.png" alt="" width="500" height="150" /></a></p><p class="p2">unwire 讀者於 2 月 14 日前結帳時輸入優惠碼「UNWIRE150」，更可享 $150 折扣優惠（須購買單一產品滿 $3,000）</p><h2 class="p2">入門推介 &#8211; IdeaPad L3i 15&#8243;</h2><p class="p2">想平價入手實用型工作電腦，你還有更多選擇，這部 IdeaPad L3i 15&#8243; 擁有更大熒幕，售價低至 HK$2,998。它給你 15.6 吋更大的超窄邊框 FHD 熒幕，而且已內置有 256GB SSD 與 Windows 10 Home 64，加上支援 Dolby Audio 喇叭系統，工作、睇片同時滿足。電腦提供長達 11 小時續航力，快速充電技術給你在 1 個小時由 0% 充電到 80%，讓你快速完成手頭上的工作。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/IdeaPad-L3i-15-88IPL301386-725x515-2.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/IdeaPad-L3i-15-88IPL301386-725x515-2-694x493.png" alt="" width="694" height="493" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/IdeaPad-L3i-15-88IPL301386-725x515-2-694x493.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/IdeaPad-L3i-15-88IPL301386-725x515-2.png 725w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-l3-gallery-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1085049" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-l3-gallery-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-l3-gallery-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-l3-gallery-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/lenovo-laptop-ideapad-l3-gallery-4.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p class="p2">原價：HK$5,058</p><p class="p2">特價：HK$2,998（6 折）</p><p class="p2">購買連結：<a href="https://lenovo.dgi7au.net/AoR9Kj" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1085045 size-full" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/126046736_309199960140873_5010468024046516166_n.png" alt="" width="500" height="150" /></a></p><p class="p2">unwire 讀者於 2 月 14 日前結帳時輸入優惠碼「UNWIRE150」，更可享 $150 折扣優惠（須購買單一產品滿 $3,000）</p><h2 class="p2">人氣 AMD 之選 &#8211; ThinkPad X13 AMD Gen 2</h2><p class="p2">ThinkPad 一直是 Lenovo 旗下熱門商務電腦系列，而這部 AMD 款的 ThinkPad X13 Gen 2 (13 吋 AMD) 配備 AMD Ryzen 5 PRO 5650U 系列處理器，搭載 16GB LPDDR4x 記憶體和 512GB SSD 儲存裝置，提供強勁效能。這部電腦極為輕薄，重量只有 1