</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Sony 與《GT 賽車》團隊開發遊戲 AI    可成為玩家對手或同伴</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/09/gran-turismo-developer-polyphony-digital-and-sony-ai-are-teasing-a-breakthrough-project/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=gran-turismo-developer-polyphony-digital-and-sony-ai-are-teasing-a-breakthrough-project</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 09 Feb 2022 07:28:28 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[GT 賽車]]></category><category><![CDATA[Polyphony]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sony Ai]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1085181</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Sony AI 日前發佈了一段預告片，宣佈將在 2 月 9 日與《GT 賽車》系列的開發商 Polyphony  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Sony AI 日前發佈了一段預告片，宣佈將在 2 月 9 日與《GT 賽車》系列的開發商 Polyphony Digital 一同公佈一個「突破性」的 AI 合作項目。有媒體推測，或許 Sony AI 和 Polyphony 將展示的這份合作項目是指在賽車遊戲 AI 方面取得的進展。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1085182" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BF917673-1672-4815-9330-2E5710EB8E3D-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BF917673-1672-4815-9330-2E5710EB8E3D-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BF917673-1672-4815-9330-2E5710EB8E3D-1280x719.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BF917673-1672-4815-9330-2E5710EB8E3D-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BF917673-1672-4815-9330-2E5710EB8E3D-1536x863.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/BF917673-1672-4815-9330-2E5710EB8E3D.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">去年年底，Sony AI 和 Polyphony 共同發佈了一篇文章，當中提及到根據視覺線索訓練的 AI 在《GT 賽車》中駕駛汽車，取得比人類駕駛員更好的成績的可能性，AI 人工智能可成為玩家對手或同伴。是次公佈的預告片中出現了《GT 賽車》系列的 Logo、「Race Together」的宣傳語，以及展示汽車發動機、方向盤和駕駛員的畫面，因此有推測認為，Sony AI 和 Polyphony 將宣佈推出的合作項目將針對在賽車遊戲 AI 方面。</span></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">🏁 COMING SOON  🏁</p><p>On 2/9, our team is excited to launch our Gaming Flagship and announce a breakthrough project in <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/AI?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#AI</a> created through a collab with Polyphony Digital Inc. (PDI) and <a href="https://twitter.com/Sony?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Sony</a> Interactive Entertainment (SIE). Enjoy this sneak peek. <a href="https://t.co/XlHvBQuu1Q">https://t.co/XlHvBQuu1Q</a></p><p>&mdash; Sony AI (@SonyAI_global) <a href="https://twitter.com/SonyAI_global/status/1490717055536050181?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 7, 2022</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">《GT 賽車 7》原訂於去年開始發售，但由於疫情關係順延到今年 3 月 4 日發售，將登陸在 PS4/PS5 平台。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_76971"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MG_pecVKq_Y?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://wccftech.com/gran-turismo-polyphony-digital-sony-ai-breakthrough-project/">Wccftech</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
